<P>
5 CLU PLAYERS NAMED ALL-DISTRICT IN SOFTBALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Five Cal Lutheran players have been selected to the All-District 3 softball 
team. Pitchers DeeAndra Pilkington and Leslie Stevens, catcher Cheryl 
Aschenbach, shortstop Dani Piotrowski and utility player Kim White were chosen 
in balloting by District 3 coaches. 
</P>
