Photo, Melissa Manchester, left, entertains crowd at the Disneyland Hotel. At 
right, Allen Boerner, who co-chaired the event, with his wife, Susan. PAMELA 
MARIN / For The Times; Photo, Fred Port, Anita Swift, Sherron Paul and Michael 
Hughes enjoy Derby Day at Remick's restaurant. ROD BOREN / For The Times 
</P>
